@startuml
actor "Scheduler\n(NiFi/Airflow)" as SCH
participant "Ingesta" as ING
participant "Kafka" as K
participant "HDFS" as H
participant "Spark" as S
participant "Cassandra" as C
participant "Hive" as HV
participant "Dashboard" as UI
participant "OpenWeather API" as OWM

SCH -> ING: Trigger (cada 15 min)
ING -> K: Publica snapshot (raw/filtered)
ING -> H: Guarda backup JSON
SCH -> S: Ejecuta procesamiento
S -> H: Lee backup / staging
S -> C: Escribe estado operativo
S -> HV: Escribe histórico
UI -> C: Lee estado actual
UI -> HV: Consulta histórico (opcional)\n(riesgo por hub 24h / top causas 24h)

== Exploración didáctica (CU-09, opcional) ==
UI -> ING: consulta_clima_hubs(api_key sesión)
ING -> OWM: HTTP OpenWeather
OWM --> ING: clima por hub
ING --> UI: tabla en Streamlit

@enduml
